title: ADS2015
description:
ADS2015.01 as 5 .rar files totaling 4.23GB.  This includes everything for a Windows 7 and Linux OS installation.  

Note the following.

The ADS program installation went fine.  The crack instructions are in Chinese.  I used Google translate to get the English version.  However I could not get the crack to work.  The translated crack instructions seem too vague and incomplete.  It seems to interchangeably use host ID, CPU ID, and MAC address as to what needs to be entered in multiple locations to crack the program.

I'm not an expert in these matters and could not figure it out.  I'm posting it here in the hope that someone who is good at this stuff can figure it out and post back clear crack instructions.

Please, someone with the right skills take a stab at it.

Thanks
